# Commands (run from repo root)

## Dev

- `pnpm dev:api` — NestJS watch mode
- `pnpm dev:web` — Vite mini app (port 5173)
- `pnpm dev:admin` — Vite admin panel
- `pnpm dev:web:tunnel` — web + ngrok for Telegram testing

## Test

- `pnpm test` — root Jest (all API unit specs)
- `pnpm test:api` — API unit tests only
- `pnpm test:api:e2e` — API e2e tests
- `pnpm test:api:cov` — API coverage

## Database (API)

- `pnpm --filter api db:migrate:dev --name <change>` — create migration
- `pnpm --filter api db:generate` — regenerate Prisma client
- `pnpm --filter api db:seed` — run seed
- `pnpm --filter api db:studio` — Prisma Studio

## Railway

- Deploy guide: `railway/README.md` (Postgres plugin + api/web/admin; set `RAILWAY_CONFIG_FILE` per service)

## Docker

- `pnpm docker:up` — Postgres + MinIO (dev)
- `pnpm docker:test-db` — test database for e2e
- `pnpm docker:test-db:down` — tear down test DB

## Build / lint

- `pnpm build` — build all apps
- `pnpm -r run lint` — lint all apps
